    lines.append("- [ ] Load testing completed against production-equivalent environment\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Response time p95 < 500ms under expected load\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] PostgreSQL query performance analyzed (no full-table scans)\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Redis cache hit rate > 80%\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Qdrant vector search latency p95 < 100ms\n\n")

    lines.append("## Documentation\n\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] [deployment.md](deployment.md) reviewed by operations team\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] [startup.md](startup.md) used to verify startup sequence\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] [troubleshooting.md](troubleshooting.md) available on-call runbook\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] [backup_restore.md](backup_restore.md) referenced in DR plan\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Architecture diagrams up to date: [docs/diagrams/](../diagrams/README.md)\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] On-call procedures documented and team notified\n\n")

    lines.append("## Post-Deployment Verification\n\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Smoke tests passing (`./scripts/smoke-tests.sh`)\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Monitor error rate for first 30 minutes post-deployment\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Verify all service integrations working (PostgreSQL, Redis, Qdrant)\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Verify n8n workflows triggering correctly (if configured)\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] OmniRoute model requests succeeding in logs\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Rollback plan validated and ready if needed\n\n")

    lines.append("## Sign-Off\n\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Technical lead approval obtained\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Security review completed\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Operations team notified of deployment window\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Deployment scheduled and communicated to stakeholders\n")
    lines.append("- [ ] Rollback procedure tested and ready\n\n")

    lines.append("## Cross-References\n\n")
    lines.append("- [configuration.md](configuration.md) — All environment variables\n")
    lines.append("- [deployment.md](deployment.md) — Deployment procedure\n")
    lines.append("- [startup.md](startup.md) — Service startup sequence\n")
    lines.append("- [monitoring.md](monitoring.md) — Alert thresholds\n")
    lines.append("- [backup_restore.md](backup_restore.md) — Backup verification\n")
    lines.append("- [troubleshooting.md](troubleshooting.md) — Issue resolution\n")

    return "".join(lines)
